<p><strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> We need another one, Roget.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Roget. I want you to pretend to be a ghost with a sheet.</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/tLMKnDa.jpg" width="500px" alt="tLMKnDa.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Part Three</span></strong>:</p>
<p><strong>&lt;Troy&gt;</strong> You around?<br />
<strong>&lt;Rogisreallyinbednow&gt;</strong> I secretly got up because my dogs pushed me out of bed, but I don't wanna hop in chat<br />
<strong>&lt;Rogisreallyinbednow&gt;</strong> sup?<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> Not much.<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> I need you to very angrily eat a spoonful of peanutbutter.<br />
<strong>&lt;Rogisreallyinbednow&gt;</strong> You pinged me for anything in part- right now?<br />
<strong>&lt;Rogisreallyinbednow&gt;</strong> aaaargh<br />
<strong>&lt;Rogisreallyinbednow&gt;</strong> ok<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> Alright. Thanks.<br />
<strong>&lt;Rogisreallyinbednow&gt;</strong> give me a minute<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> Take all the time you need.</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/cL5q4XU.jpg" width="500px" alt="cL5q4XU.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Part Four</span></strong>:</p>
<p><strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Roget<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Hey.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> You here?<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> TroyL<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> hi<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> I need you to be very unimpressed with a banana.<br />
<strong>&lt;vezaz&gt;</strong> hey troyl<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> &#8230; stand by<br />
<strong>&lt;vezaz&gt;</strong> why is your dog mooning the camera<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Thanks, Roget.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> And the dog is awesome, there.<br />
<strong>&lt;vezaz&gt;</strong> troyl what on earth is that for<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> vezaz because before the picture I was rubbing her belly</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/tQqJl0f.jpg" width="500px" alt="tQqJl0f.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Part Five</span></strong>:</p>
<p><strong>RogetSOTIRED</strong> wrenches self up from desk<br />
<strong>RogetSOTIRED</strong> gone for reals now<br />
<strong>&lt;~TroyL&gt;</strong> Oh, Roget.<br />
<strong>&lt;~TroyL&gt;</strong> Before you go.<br />
<strong>&lt;@thedeadlymoose&gt;</strong> Troy, you are the cruelest. :|<br />
<strong>&lt;~TroyL&gt;</strong> I'm gonna need you to pretend to be a ninja using a black t-shirt.</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/SAeZ06s.jpg" width="500px" alt="SAeZ06s.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Part Six</span></strong>:</p>
<p><strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> But Roget?<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> I'm going to need you to be very upset over having to choose between two different sodas.<br />
<strong>&lt;Roget&gt;</strong> Can one of them be tea?<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> Is it in a can?<br />
<strong>&lt;Roget&gt;</strong> yes<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> Then yes. Please look back and forth, then appear extremely conflicted.</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/dkog519.jpg" width="500px" alt="dkog519.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Part Seven</span></strong>:</p>
<p><strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> Roget.<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> Hey, Roget.<br />
<strong>&lt;Roget&gt;</strong> aye<br />
<strong>&lt;TroyL&gt;</strong> I need you to glare angrily at your sock, then challenge it to a duel.<br />
<strong>&lt;Roget&gt;</strong> k</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/dgkdyuG.jpg" width="500px" alt="dgkdyuG.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/1uI2Djb.jpg" width="500px" alt="1uI2Djb.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Part Eight</span></strong>:</p>
<p><strong>&lt;@kaktus&gt;</strong> TroyL: surprise <a href="http://imgur.com/GzzFGOY">http://imgur.com/GzzFGOY</a><br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Already saw it, Kaktus.<br />
<strong>&lt;@kaktus&gt;</strong> Drat<br />
<strong>&lt;@kaktus&gt;</strong> Foiled by the upscroll<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Man. I just realized how much I want more Roget based .gifs.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Roget. ROGET!<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> aye<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> I'm going to need you to make a .gif of yourself blowing out an NES cartridge. Bonus points for perfect loop.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Double bonus points if it's a Wisdom Tree game.<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> I don't know how to make gifs but I can send a video to kaktus to make into a gif<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Perfect.<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> Can I do color dreams<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> does that count<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Which game, Roget?<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> Metal Fighter*<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Ugghhhh.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Uggggghhhhhh.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Do you have Gauntlet?<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> nope<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> I have bible adventures tho<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> :D<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Which Bible Adventures?<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Blue or Black?<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> blue<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> duh<br />
<strong>&lt;@Roget&gt;</strong> its not really bible adventures if its not blue<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Very nice.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> That'll work, yes.<br />
<strong>&lt;&amp;TroyL&gt;</strong> Kaktus, I have an important job for you.</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/agent-lament-s-personnel-file/Q2oftcE.gif" width="500px" alt="Q2oftcE.gif" class="image" /></div>
